  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Ali Akbor OBE appointed to the Grenfell Tower Inquiry Panel
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The Prime Minister has confirmed the appointment of Ali Akbor OBE to the Grenfell Tower Inquiry Panel for Phase 2 of its work.</p>

  </div>
